title: Dakine Tempest Glove
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Tempest Glove in Black.
Tempest Features:
- Insert: Gore Tex® Waterproof / Breathable
- Palm: Touch screen compatible leather
- Shell: 4-way stretch nylon
- Insulation: Primaloft [ 113g ]
- Lining: 230g Fleece / 400g Pile
- Cuff Closure: Adjustable hook and loop
